item.title: CVE-2017-5234|2024-08-05T14:55:35.651Z -- rapid7 -- insight%20collector
item.description: Rapid7 Insight Collector installers prior to version 1.0.16 contain a DLL preloading vulnerability, wherein it is possible for the installer to load a malicious DLL located in the current working directory of the installer.
